1512
00:58:33,780 --> 00:58:35,700
[I'm leaving then, Bro.]

1513
00:58:35,310 --> 00:58:36,370
-Go for it!
-Go for it!

1514
00:58:36,240 --> 00:58:38,280
[Go for it, Dex!]
[Go for it, Jung Hae-in!]

1515
00:58:36,370 --> 00:58:38,240
-Go for it, Dex!
-Go for it, Jung Hae-in!

1516
00:58:38,240 --> 00:58:39,740
