1655
01:04:08,990 --> 01:04:10,260
-Steak.
-Steak.

1656
01:04:10,840 --> 01:04:13,060
[One more]

1657
01:04:12,160 --> 01:04:13,520
-One more?
-Yeah, one more.

1658
