1680
01:05:10,210 --> 01:05:10,870
Delicious.

1681
01:05:14,890 --> 01:05:16,020
[Takes a big bite]

1682
01:05:16,980 --> 01:05:18,700
[Wonderful]

1683
01:05:19,440 --> 01:05:22,620
